	('Bruant des neiges', 'Plectrophenax nivalis', 'Animalia', 'Chordata', 'Aves', 'Toundra', 'Herbivore', 'LC', 'Stable', 'Petit passereau nichant plus au nord que tout autre oiseau terrestre.', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/Snow_Bunting_%28Plectrophenax_nivalis%29%2C_Thule%2C_Greenland_1.jpg/960px-Snow_Bunting_%28Plectrophenax_nivalis%29%2C_Thule%2C_Greenland_1.jpg'),
